Libre Source Clause

Subject to the terms and conditions of this license, all redistributions, modified
and unmodified, must include all source code encompassing the redistributed software and 
all 3rd-party non-system software dynamically/statically linked with the redistributed
software, as well as the tools required to build an executable form of the software, in
its full functionality.

Limited Libre Source Clause

Subject to the terms and conditions of this license, all redistributions  modified 
and unmodified, within 3 years of availability of the software it was derived from, must
include all source code encompassing the redistributed software and all 3rd-party non-system
software dynamically/statically linked with the redistributed software, as well as the tools
required to build an executable form of the software, in its full functionality.
